---
title: Easy Asian Chicken & Pickled Carrot Salad with Coriander & Crispy Shallots
description: This vibrant Asian salad is a refreshing, flavour-packed dish. Tender, caramelised chicken breast is coated in a sweet chilli and soy glaze, balanced with tangy quick-pickled carrot and radish, crisp lettuce, and fresh herbs. Topped with a drizzle of zingy dressing, it’s a perfect harmony of bright flavours and textures for a light but satiating meal.
